dr.geo.cartogram
Class CartogramMapping

java.lang.Object
  dr.geo.cartogram.CartogramMapping

public class CartogramMapping
extends java.lang.Object

Provides basic functionality for output from Mark Newman's 'cartogram' - Reads resulting flat text file - Uses bilinear interpolation to map (real space x, real space y) -> (cartogram x, cartogram y)

Author:
Marc A. Suchard
